title: 3 Pole + Pre-earth CA Series Line Plug
blurb:
Hirschmann C16-1 Series or similar connectors offer 4 or 7 way (3 and 6 with plus a P.E. - or pre-engaging - earth contact). For further technical information see specifications. A quality industry-standard connector.
- Electrical:                           3 Pole + PE
- Contact Resistance:             <5mohm
- Temperature range:              -40°C to + 100°C
- Housing:                             Polyamide 6.6
- Strain Relief:                       Screw clamp/Ring & Gland Nut (9mm)
